{"parentUuid":"5300778c-8a31-4b34-9fed-df73431a3082","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"355fde58-9f2e-494b-a7ef-2adac2674b7c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about \"Microsoft 365 Copilot\" that appears in the bottom-right corner of their Windows taskbar/system tray, and they want to remove it to keep their computer clean.\n\nThis is not a coding question - it's a general Windows/software question. Let me answer directly based on what I know.\n\nMicrosoft 365 Copilot is an AI assistant integrated into Microsoft 365 apps (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, etc.) and can appear as a taskbar icon or system tray icon in Windows. It's part of Microsoft's push to integrate AI into their products.\n\nLet me give the user practical advice on how to remove/disable it.","signature":"355fde58-9f2e-494b-a7ef-2adac2674b7c"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":26693,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":478,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"fa501918-d83f-43fd-8b2b-562be9dee6dc","timestamp":"2026-05-18T17:00:30.021Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\ClaudeCode workspace","sessionId":"a5a364d3-32e3-4c52-8950-4b420638b25f","version":"2.1.143","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"fa501918-d83f-43fd-8b2b-562be9dee6dc","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"355fde58-9f2e-494b-a7ef-2adac2674b7c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Microsoft 365 Copilot** 是微软推的 AI 助手，集成在 Office 全家桶里（Word、Excel、PPT 等），右下角那个图标是它的快捷入口。微软通过 Windows Update 或 Office 更新自动塞进来的，不是你自己装的。\n\n**去掉它的方法：**\n\n1. **卸载 Copilot 应用**\n   - 设置 → 应用 → 已安装的应用 → 搜索 \"Copilot\" → 卸载 \"Microsoft Copilot\" 和 \"Microsoft 365 Copilot\"（如果有的话）\n\n2. **从任务栏隐藏/关闭**\n   - 右键任务栏 → 任务栏设置 → 找到 \"Copilot\" → 关闭开关\n\n3. **禁用 Office 里的 Copilot**\n   - 打开任意 Office 应用 → 文件 → 选项 → 信任中心 → 信任中心设置 → 隐私选项 → 隐私设置 → 关闭\"启用连接体验\"相关选项（这会禁用所有 AI 功能）\n\n4. **组策略彻底禁用**（Win 10/11 专业版以上）\n   - `Win + R` → `gpedit.msc` → 用户配置 → 管理模板 → Windows 组件 → Windows Copilot → 启用\"关闭 Windows Copilot\"\n\n5. **如果不想让 Windows 自动装这些**\n   - 设置 → 个性化 → 设备使用 → 把\"显示 Microsoft 365 的推荐内容\"关掉\n\n最简单粗暴的方式是**第 1 步直接卸载**，不影响 Office 正常使用。如果注册表/组策略那里彻底禁用，后续 Windows Update 也不会再给你偷偷装回来。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":26693,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":478,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"05b07de3-035e-4009-bf70-70bfcc8460d4","timestamp":"2026-05-18T17:00:41.404Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\ClaudeCode workspace","sessionId":"a5a364d3-32e3-4c52-8950-4b420638b25f","version":"2.1.143","gitBranch":"main"}
